Description: 
    This package provides a wrapper for the CAISO locational marginal price 
    (LMP) datasets using the Grid Status API. The package allows users to 
    access node-level LMP data concerning the California eletrical grid and
    integrate it with data concerning California's transmission lines to 
    identity areas of high congestion. Additionally, the package provides tools 
    to visualize and analyze the LMP data to produce insightful and effective 
    results concerning California eletrical grid congestion.
